title: DAZ3D - Poser - LY Karine (DAZ 17785) DIM G2F
description:
LY Karine is a high quality character. She is a beautiful woman with a strong warrior shape. Powerful and shapely, she is a perfect accompaniment to Olympia 6. A custom character carefully crafted to look and work wonderfully in DAZ 4.6+ and Poser 9+ (via the DSON Importer for Poser).

Karine has nine lovely makeup options, 18 lip colors (nine matte and nine glossy), and nine beautiful custom eye colors. Of course, she also has the basic nude makeup option and nude glossy or matte lips
